{
  "stem": "2946.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, when I arrived in Theresienstadt, there was-- there was a-- there was talking about that some young Jewish men had connections with the outside world, were sending letters out to the Aryan Czech population, were even getting some mail from the outside.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were caught, and 12 of them were hanged publicly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew the man who was-- he was a butcher, and he was assigned to do the hanging for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fischer was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a member of the-- but he was mentally disturbed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they asked him to-- to do the executions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were publicly 12 of them executed, but I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came after this happened-- shortly after.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everybody told us about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was an incident.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day they had the whole ghetto moved about three kilometers from the ghetto, and we were in a valley standing, this-- it could have been a big pond before, but there was no water in it-- and it was a-- a little-- not-- like hills around the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, it dried out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The water was taken out or dried out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were standing there, the whole of Theresienstadt, I don't know how many-- 1,000 of us-- standing all day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were-- there were soldiers on the embankment with guns facing us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And allegedly, we found out, towards the evening, that the Germans were talking to the-- this is what I heard-- to the Red Cross in Switzerland to buy our live out for money.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were arguing back and forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By the end-- by the evening, I guess the deal came over and we were asked to march back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
